# Profiling data placeholder
# 
# 目录结构:
# compute/{device}/{model_name}/
#   - attention.csv
#   - mlp.csv
#   - expert.csv
#   - eplb.csv
#
# network/{network_device}/
#   - all_reduce.csv     (NVLink all-reduce profiling)
#   - send_recv.csv      (PP send/recv profiling)
#   - expert_comm.csv    (EP all-to-all profiling)
#   - rdma_transfer.csv  (RDMA 传输 profiling, 后续采集)
